{"title":"深情诉于这个春天","authors":["宋晓杰"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情诉于这个春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋晓杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果泪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是苦涩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是星星为之逊色的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果眼神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是恐惧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是死神望而却步的安详"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果拥抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是团聚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是牵念出发的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果奔赴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是炮火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是拯救苦难与爱的战场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是缠绵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是溪水洞穿冰层的歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果手势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是挥别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是意志无声的起航"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果月色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是沉睡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是咫尺之间不眠的守望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是笑脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是嘹亮的祈祷和哀伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果女人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是懦弱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是意志无可比拟的坚强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是流星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是精神恒久闪烁的天堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果感动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是奢侈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是春风化雨般的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是抚慰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是人类最温暖的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二○○三，温煦的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我感到决心、品格、勇气、尊严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟随关怀的潜流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与蓬勃的绿色一起动情地生长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二○○三，永久的铭刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到一盏盏信念的灯笼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注解短暂的暗夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一个洁白、丰沛、坚劲的民族照亮！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}